@startuml SD-01_User_Registration

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 17
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 300

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
    FontStyle plain
}

skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}

skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #333333
    ArrowThickness 1
    ArrowFontColor #000000
    ArrowFontSize 16
    LifeLineBorderColor #333333
    LifeLineBorderThickness 1
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
    GroupBorderColor #888888
    GroupBorderThickness 1
    GroupHeaderFontColor #000000
    DividerBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
    DividerFontColor #000000
    DividerBorderColor #AAAAAA
    DividerBorderThickness 1
    BoxBorderColor #888888
    BoxBorderThickness 1
    ParticipantBorderThickness 1
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #999999
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}

' ─── Participants ───────────────────────────────────────
actor       "User"              as User
participant "Web UI"            as UI
participant "Auth Controller"   as Ctrl
participant "Auth Service"      as Svc
database    "Database"          as DB

' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Form Submission ==
' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

User -> UI  : Fill in name, email, password\nClick "Create Account"
UI   -> UI  : Validate fields (Zod schema)

alt Validation fails
    UI --> User : Show inline field errors
end

UI -> Ctrl : POST /auth/register\n{ name, email, password }

' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Registration Logic ==
' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Ctrl -> Svc : register(dto)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : findOne({ email })
activate DB
DB --> Svc : result
deactivate DB

alt Email already registered
    Svc --> Ctrl : 409 Conflict
    Ctrl --> UI  : 409 Email already registered
    UI  --> User : Show error message
end

Svc -> Svc : bcrypt.hash(password)
Svc -> DB  : save(User)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : savedUser { id, name, email }
deactivate DB

Svc -> DB  : save(Organization)\nsave(OrganizationMember, role: ADMIN)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : savedOrg, savedMember
deactivate DB

Svc -> Svc : Sign accessToken + refreshToken (JWT)

Svc --> Ctrl : AuthResponse\n{ accessToken, refreshToken, user }
deactivate Svc

' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Success ==
' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Ctrl --> UI   : 201 Created + AuthResponse
UI   --> User : Toast "Account created!"\nRedirect to /overview

@enduml
